<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA26">
<l>ñāṉṟa kuḻaṟcaṭaikaḷ poṉvaraipōṉ miṉṉuvaṉa</l>
<l>pōṉṟa kaṟaimiṭaṟṟāṉ poṉmārpiṉ - ñāṉṟeṅku</l>
<l>mikkayalē tōṉṟa viḷaṅki miḷirumē</l>
<l>yakkayalē vaitta varavu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[His] matted hair in hanging locks flash like a golden mountain.</l>
<l>He has a similar spot on [his] throat. On [his] golden chest, hanging,</l>
<l>shining so that is appears very close everywhere turns</l>
<l>the snake that is put close to the Rudrākṣa [beads].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
